  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　―― <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/1864e1c776c757b8a2321f58d914e3a6.webp?t=1773980016\" width=30 height=29 /></span>も無き少女はあなたとなり、あなたは名も無き少女となる。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53f612598ef0576621de8533fb041041.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >アブセンテッドエイジは、非戦闘時はARPG、戦闘中はSRPG仕立ての</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ローグライク戦闘で展開される新感覚のミックスジャンルゲームです。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵に接触したり、攻撃を仕掛ける(仕掛けられる)と、周囲を巻き込んでシームレスにターン戦闘に移行します。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/eda2ca7341f0025f26d81e32d5afd203.avif?t=1773980016\" width=487 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百におよぶ個性豊かなスキル/アイテムの応酬を切り抜け、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色んな衣装に着せ替えながら手ごわいモンスターたちをなぎ倒しましょう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公たち『茶道バンド部』によるインタラクティブなBGM表現が、いっそう物語を盛り上げます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★本作は前作「幽玄の章」の続編にあたり、クリアデータの引継ぎも可能です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　また好評のチュートリアルは今作も完備。初めて遊ぶ方でも安心です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今作では、物語で絆を育んだ友を呼び出し共闘する「アシスト召喚」、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一時交代し切り抜ける「チェンジ召喚」の使い所も戦略のカギを握ります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半チャージ攻撃、カウンター、ジャストガード、ヒットストップずらしなど</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ジャンルに囚われない高等テクニックも使いこなして、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ぜひ、あなただけの最強の魅せプレイを見せつけてください。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作は別記のガイドラインに従う限り、自由に実況プレイを公開できます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/3d6967f5dd9c8371d2740865fd831dcc.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >記憶と実体を失い、記憶の異世界「禁領」で目覚めた幽霊の少女(あなた)。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは、禁領で出会った精霊タルトと共に記憶を集め――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自分がこの夏に開かれる一大音楽イベント「超楽祭」を夢見る</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"カレン\" というトランペット奏者だったこと、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >そして、世間で死亡説が流れる今も</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >バンド仲間たちが懸命にあなたを捜索し続けていることを知ります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/78e91540d6b34d30eded99248024eb6f.avif?t=1773980016\" width=400 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは、街や禁領で心を巣食う謎の怪異</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ゲンガーたちとの激戦の末、失くした心の欠片の半数を奪還。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密組織「エリシオ教会」の精霊使いヤヨイの助力もあり、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは不完全ながらも現世に実体化するすべを得ました。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >そして、舞台は \"カレン\" の思い出が多く眠る学校へ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >しかしそこでは、あなたの過去を握るさらなる異変が、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >記憶のうみの底で待ち受けているのでした――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/57d028cd4a9c7ecdf09e63c604ba00a5.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆仲間との連携</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強力な反撃スキルで囲まれた状況をチャンスに変える「ハヤト」に、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自律行動する設置砲台を軸にした籠城戦を得意とする「スズ」など……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたが物語を通じて育んだ仲間との絆は、精霊石を介して禁領に顕現し</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒険を強力にサポートしてくれます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装備した精霊石によりARPG中のアクションも変化。戦略の幅が広がります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたの相棒、精霊タルトの戦闘スタイルを瞬時に切り替える精霊術も健在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加されたスキルツリーによって、追撃や自動回復など、長所をさらに伸ばすことも可能です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c482b27958b4dceafa7430ddad3acd9a.avif?t=1773980016\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆豊富な装備品・衣装着せ替え</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新装備の立ち絵はすべて新規描き下ろし。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今作も状態異常差分や装備の着せ替えパーツが爆裂に豊富です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同装備を入手する度に上がっていく装備の熟練度(+値)は</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ロストしても維持されるため、どんどん新しいコーデを試してみましょう。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/bcc07916aff62268e646780729928552.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→『AbsentedAge:アブセンテッドエイジ ～亡霊少女のローグライクアクションSRPG -幽玄の章-』（AbsentedAge: Squarebound）</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　―― <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/1864e1c776c757b8a2321f58d914e3a6.webp?t=1773980016\" width=30 height=29 /></span>も無き少女はあなたとなり、あなたは名も無き少女となる。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53f612598ef0576621de8533fb041041.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >アブセンテッドエイジは、非戦闘時はARPG、戦闘中はSRPG仕立ての</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ローグライク戦闘で展開される新感覚のミックスジャンルゲームです。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵に接触したり、攻撃を仕掛ける(仕掛けられる)と、周囲を巻き込んでシームレスにターン戦闘に移行します。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/eda2ca7341f0025f26d81e32d5afd203.avif?t=1773980016\" width=487 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/53e2b05d7d49c47a255d41d2b6956979.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百におよぶ個性豊かなスキル/アイテムの応酬を切り抜け、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色んな衣装に着せ替えながら手ごわいモンスターたちをなぎ倒しましょう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公たち『茶道バンド部』によるインタラクティブなBGM表現が、いっそう物語を盛り上げます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★本作は前作「幽玄の章」の続編にあたり、クリアデータの引継ぎも可能です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　また好評のチュートリアルは今作も完備。初めて遊ぶ方でも安心です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今作では、物語で絆を育んだ友を呼び出し共闘する「アシスト召喚」、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一時交代し切り抜ける「チェンジ召喚」の使い所も戦略のカギを握ります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c2d90e6fe9ccfc7f29daca79209a417f.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半チャージ攻撃、カウンター、ジャストガード、ヒットストップずらしなど</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ジャンルに囚われない高等テクニックも使いこなして、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ぜひ、あなただけの最強の魅せプレイを見せつけてください。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作は別記のガイドラインに従う限り、自由に実況プレイを公開できます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/3d6967f5dd9c8371d2740865fd831dcc.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >記憶と実体を失い、記憶の異世界「禁領」で目覚めた幽霊の少女(あなた)。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは、禁領で出会った精霊タルトと共に記憶を集め――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自分がこの夏に開かれる一大音楽イベント「超楽祭」を夢見る</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"カレン\" というトランペット奏者だったこと、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >そして、世間で死亡説が流れる今も</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >バンド仲間たちが懸命にあなたを捜索し続けていることを知ります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/78e91540d6b34d30eded99248024eb6f.avif?t=1773980016\" width=400 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは、街や禁領で心を巣食う謎の怪異</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ゲンガーたちとの激戦の末、失くした心の欠片の半数を奪還。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密組織「エリシオ教会」の精霊使いヤヨイの助力もあり、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたは不完全ながらも現世に実体化するすべを得ました。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >そして、舞台は \"カレン\" の思い出が多く眠る学校へ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >しかしそこでは、あなたの過去を握るさらなる異変が、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >記憶のうみの底で待ち受けているのでした――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/57d028cd4a9c7ecdf09e63c604ba00a5.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆仲間との連携</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強力な反撃スキルで囲まれた状況をチャンスに変える「ハヤト」に、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自律行動する設置砲台を軸にした籠城戦を得意とする「スズ」など……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたが物語を通じて育んだ仲間との絆は、精霊石を介して禁領に顕現し</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒険を強力にサポートしてくれます。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装備した精霊石によりARPG中のアクションも変化。戦略の幅が広がります。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9b387ae1f1586f0d1e44ea5a892ae41e.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >あなたの相棒、精霊タルトの戦闘スタイルを瞬時に切り替える精霊術も健在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追加されたスキルツリーによって、追撃や自動回復など、長所をさらに伸ばすことも可能です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/c482b27958b4dceafa7430ddad3acd9a.avif?t=1773980016\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆豊富な装備品・衣装着せ替え</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新装備の立ち絵はすべて新規描き下ろし。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今作も状態異常差分や装備の着せ替えパーツが爆裂に豊富です。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同装備を入手する度に上がっていく装備の熟練度(+値)は</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ロストしても維持されるため、どんどん新しいコーデを試してみましょう。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/9e9bef79d7e954eee07efd5a1ce92915.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.poster.avif?t=1773980016\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.webm?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/f8432449069858eaa88b4276bf4ae578.mp4?t=1773980016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/5d7dfc2394963c94c404aaf1cb21585f.webp?t=1773980016\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/705c7fa6aed2e114807a0c5e9a1a26b4.webp?t=1773980016\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184650/extras/bcc07916aff62268e646780729928552.webp?t=1773980016\" width=302 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→『AbsentedAge:アブセンテッドエイジ ～亡霊少女のローグライクアクションSRPG -幽玄の章-』（AbsentedAge: Squarebound）</p>",
